== 兒童與青少年的BMI ==
BMI並不单单適用於成年人。對於成長中的儿童，我们亦可利用他们的BMI來推算他们是否超重。BMI計算式亦適用於15-20岁的人，但他们的過重及過輕定義方法，就不是用固定的BMI決定。這是因為兒童青少年正處發育期，BMI隨著發育在變動，若使用一個固定數值，容易造成錯誤判斷。

很多國家及地區每年都會為當地的兒童作身高和體重的統計。這些統計數據，都須先調查族群中健康兒童的BMI分布，從而再根據這個分布，推算出當地兒童的過重及過輕指標。一般來說，都會採用統計出來的平均BMI及其[[標準差|標準差]]值，再計算出其[[常態分布|常態分布]]的最高5%及最低5%作為過重及過輕指標。另一方面，其BMI位於常態分布的85%-95%區段的兒童，會被視為有超重的風險。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Capter 2. Use of Percentiles and Z-Scores in Anthropometry. In Handbook of Anthropometry|last=Wang|first=Youfa|publisher=Springer|year=2012|isbn=978-1-4419-1787-4|location=New York|pages=29}}</ref>

== 肥胖悖論==
早期臨床研究觀察顯示，在慢性病患中，BMI較低者的[[死亡率|死亡率]]比BMI較高者來得高。最早是在1999年發現過重與[[肥胖症|肥胖]]的透析[[血液透析|洗腎]]患者中較長的[[存活率|存活率]]，<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Obesity-survival paradox-still a controversy?|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17991192/|last=Schmidt|first=Darren S.|last2=Salahudeen|first2=Abdulla K.|date=2007-11|journal=Seminars in Dialysis|issue=6|doi=10.1111/j.1525-139X.2007.00349.x|volume=20|pages=486–492|issn=0894-0959|pmid=17991192}}</ref> 後來也在心血管疾病病患<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Reverse epidemiology of conventional cardiovascular risk factors in patients with chronic heart failure|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15093881/|last=Kalantar-Zadeh|first=Kamyar|last2=Block|first2=Gladys|date=2004-04-21|journal=Journal of the American College of Cardiology|issue=8|doi=10.1016/j.jacc.2003.11.039|volume=43|pages=1439–1444|issn=0735-1097|pmid=15093881|last3=Horwich|first3=Tamara|last4=Fonarow|first4=Gregg C.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Meta-analysis of the relation of body mass index to all-cause and cardiovascular mortality and hospitalization in patients with chronic heart failure|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25772740|last=Sharma|first=Abhishek|last2=Lavie|first2=Carl J.|date=2015-05-15|journal=The American Journal of Cardiology|issue=10|doi=10.1016/j.amjcard.2015.02.024|volume=115|pages=1428–1434|issn=1879-1913|pmid=25772740|last3=Borer|first3=Jeffrey S.|last4=Vallakati|first4=Ajay|last5=Goel|first5=Sunny|last6=Lopez-Jimenez|first6=Francisco|last7=Arbab-Zadeh|first7=Armin|last8=Mukherjee|first8=Debabrata|last9=Lazar|first9=Jason M.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Association of overweight and obesity with patient mortality after acute myocardial infarction: a meta-analysis of prospective studies|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26338077/|last=Wang|first=L.|last2=Liu|first2=W.|date=2016-02|journal=International Journal of Obesity (2005)|issue=2|doi=10.1038/ijo.2015.176|volume=40|pages=220–228|issn=1476-5497|pmid=26338077|last3=He|first3=X.|last4=Chen|first4=Y.|last5=Lu|first5=J.|last6=Liu|first6=K.|last7=Cao|first7=K.|last8=Yin|first8=P.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The obesity paradox in acute coronary syndrome: a meta-analysis|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s10654-014-9961-9|last=Niedziela|first=Jacek|last2=Hudzik|first2=Bartosz|date=2014-11|journal=European Journal of Epidemiology|issue=11|doi=10.1007/s10654-014-9961-9|volume=29|pages=801–812|language=en|issn=0393-2990|pmc=PMC4220102|pmid=25354991|last3=Niedziela|first3=Natalia|last4=Gąsior|first4=Mariusz|last5=Gierlotka|first5=Marek|last6=Wasilewski|first6=Jarosław|last7=Myrda|first7=Krzysztof|last8=Lekston|first8=Andrzej|last9=Poloński|first9=Lech}}</ref>、{{le|護理之家|Nursing home care}}的老邁住民<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Inverse relationship between body mass index and mortality in older nursing home residents: a meta-analysis of 19,538 elderly subjects|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26252230/|last=Veronese|first=N.|last2=Cereda|first2=E.|date=2015-11|journal=Obesity Reviews: An Official Journal of the International Association for the Study of Obesity|issue=11|doi=10.1111/obr.12309|volume=16|pages=1001–1015|issn=1467-789X|pmid=26252230|last3=Solmi|first3=M.|last4=Fowler|first4=S. A.|last5=Manzato|first5=E.|last6=Maggi|first6=S.|last7=Manu|first7=P.|last8=Abe|first8=E.|last9=Hayashi|first9=K.}}</ref>以及[[慢性阻塞性肺病|慢性阻塞性肺病]]（COPD）病患<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Body Mass Index and Mortality in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease: A Meta-Analysis|url=https://dx.plos.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0043892|last=Cao|first=Chao|last2=Wang|first2=Ran|date=2012-08-24|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=8|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0043892|editor-last=Simpson|editor-first=Colin|volume=7|pages=e43892|language=en|issn=1932-6203|pmc=PMC3427325|pmid=22937118|last3=Wang|first3=Jianmiao|last4=Bunjhoo|first4=Hansvin|last5=Xu|first5=Yongjian|last6=Xiong|first6=Weining}}</ref>中觀察到此現象，這稱為{{le|肥胖悖論|obesity paradox}}。

近年來發現，老年族群亦有此一現象。但根據[[國民營養健康狀況變遷調查|國民營養健康狀況變遷調查]]資料顯示，老年族群中所觀察到的BMI低死亡風險較高現象，是因為BMI低其實反映肌肉量比較少的狀況，因此BMI低亦反映肌肉少（或[[肌肉减少症|肌肉减少症]]）的健康風險。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Abdominal Obesity and Low Skeletal Muscle Mass Jointly Predict Total Mortality and Cardiovascular Mortality in an Elderly Asian Population|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26590913/|last=Chuang|first=Shao-Yuan|last2=Hsu|first2=Yueh-Ying|date=2016-08|journal=The Journals of Gerontology. Series A, Biological Sciences and Medical Sciences|issue=8|doi=10.1093/gerona/glv192|volume=71|pages=1049–1055|issn=1758-535X|pmid=26590913|last3=Chen|first3=Rosalind Chia-Yu|last4=Liu|first4=Wen-Ling|last5=Pan|first5=Wen-Harn}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://udn.com/news/story/7016/1423759-國衛院：肌肉多-降低死亡風險的關鍵|title=國衛院：肌肉多 降低死亡風險的關鍵|last=龔善美、郭敏政|first=|date=2016-01-06|work=常春月刊{{!}}聯合新聞網|accessdate=2016-03-16}}</ref>

